title: 820-3209 does not work USB and TUNDERBOLT
message: I made the exchange L4620,D4610/11, L4600, D4600,R9401, U4600 and C4695 (short).Replaces the doors too.  But it didn't have an effect, I imagine it is the PCH with bad solder ?

title: 820-3209 does not work USB and TUNDERBOLT
message:
None of USB ports working?
The small coils in series with data lines, better to bypass with tiny wires.

title: 820-3209 does not work USB and TUNDERBOLT
message: the I/O power port is working. Strange the two ports J4600 and J9400 do not work. I identified the C4695 in short, it seems that it suffered a big short in this region, I think it is not worth to continue.

title: 820-3209 does not work USB and TUNDERBOLT
message:
Do you note any damage on USB ports pins?
Any history about USB device damaging the board?
Check diode mode to ground on all USB data lines.
